RE Invoices Cc I coded the King and Spalding invoices in IPAYIT yesterday Before coding I had to forward the invoices to Ben for his approval So they should be processed and paid soon through IPAYIT Thanks Tonya Original Message From Wright Alice Sent Tuesday November AM To Garcia Julie A Dennis Tonya Cc Mann Kay Subject Invoices Importance High Good morning I forwarded to you over the last three weeks approximately to invoices for codingKay Mann wants to resolve these invoices today Will you please code the invoices as the following or return them to me My last day at Enron is tomorrow pm so if you dont get them to me please process them and inform Kay Mann of the status Coral Energy Cost Center Project Blue Dog Split between Cost Centers and Midway Energy WBS C or Cost Center second choice Thank you very much for your prompt attention to this matter Alice Wright Assistant to Kay Mann Smith St EBA Houston Texas Tel Fax
